fields.name: Rebel Beans Cold Brew Coffee 125ml
fields.description: A perfect combination of coffee beans, a blend with flavors such as chocolate, berries and citrus fruits. Best cold brew coffee in Amsterdam!

fields.name: Milky Way Espresso Blend - 250gr
fields.description: Milky Way is our favorite espresso blend, which we also offer to business customers. This recipe is perfect for espresso, but you can also use it for filter coffee. The beans from Colombia and El Salvador go well together and offer you a clean, nutty, fruity taste.

fields.name: Cherry Ripe Espresso Blend - 250gr
fields.description: This blend is one of our favorites. We used coffee beans from El Salvador and Ethiopia for a balanced taste.

fields.name: Colombia Narino - 250gr
fields.description:
Meet Liberator, from Colombia's southwestern region of Narino. A very turbulent, but nevertheless very beautiful area of ​​Colombia. Expect very clean and clear flavors of terroir in this coffee.
Productor Colombia buys from multiple farmers throughout Narino, and we've combined specific coffee beans to create the flavor profile we love - a sweet, complex, and mellow citrus flavor.

fields.name: Dark Horse Blend - 250gr
fields.description: This blend has Guatemala and El Salvador coffee beans. Huehuetenango is located in western Guatemala and the coffee grown here is considered some of the best. This region also has one of three non-volcanic soils. This limestone soil has a high PH value. Usually this is not what you want, but Huehuetenango coffee beans make very tasty espressos. At high altitudes, around 1200mt, coffee cherries develop slowly, which means that nutrition is in the coffee.

fields.name: Brazil Fazenda Ferrinha - 250gr
fields.description: This lot comes from Minas Gerais, Brazil. Fazenda Serrinha farm is owned by Jose Maria de Oliveira. This particular batch comes from a project on the farm called 'Para Ela' that focuses on the financial empowerment of women. This batch is sorted and selected by a team of women who receive 50% higher wages than the average in the region, which contrasts with the usual gender pay gap.

fields.name: Filter Coffee Blend - 250gr
fields.description:
We know how much you love Sundays, so we've got this mix for you all day long. It's easy on your taste buds with vanilla and other brown spices and caramel. Crystal clear aromas come with these coffee beans.

Grind 70 grams of Rebel Beans filter coffee beans with 1 liter of water for a perfect coffee recipe.

fields.name: Espresso Blend - 250gr
fields.description:
We have prepared you a morning coffee blend with Brazilian and Costa Rican beans. With a hint of citrus with each sip, a strong body and rich aroma will amaze you.

Espresso recipe
- 20 grams Rebel Beans espresso blend
- 40 grams of coffee in your cup
- Brew your coffee for 25-27 seconds
